# DOOT Client Environment Configuration

# API Base URL (auto-detected in production, set for custom deployment)
# VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:3000

# ==================== TURN SERVER CONFIGURATION ====================
# TURN servers ensure WebRTC calls work behind NAT/firewalls
# Default: Uses free Metered.ca TURN servers (included in code)
# For production with high volume, consider paid TURN services

# Custom TURN Server (optional)
# VITE_TURN_URL=turn:your-turn-server.com:3478
# VITE_TURN_USERNAME=your-username
# VITE_TURN_CREDENTIAL=your-credential

# Multiple TURN servers (for better reliability)
# VITE_TURN_URL_2=turn:backup-turn-server.com:3478
# VITE_TURN_USERNAME_2=backup-username
# VITE_TURN_CREDENTIAL_2=backup-credential
